videos.description: Ryan Schwieger and Jaelin Llewellyln paced the Princeton offense scoring 16 and 14 points, respectively, as the Tigers defeated Penn, 63-58.
videos.headline: Highlights: Princeton 63, Penn 54  - Via Ivy League

videos.description: 2020 began with a road win at the Palestra against Pennsylvania and a 1-0 start to Ivy League play. Round two versus the Quakers is this Friday at 5 p.m. on ESPNU!
videos.headline: Princeton Basketball: Hard Cuts | Season 3 - Episode 10  - Via Ivy League
